fsSources.title: Marriage record, Horace Cleaves and Almina M. Stoddard, page 1, volume 1, Sheboygan County, Wisconsin
fsSources.notes: Place of marriage Greenbush, Sheboygan County; date 22 September 1852; groom Horace Cleaves, birthplace Elbridge, Onandagua County, New York; parents John and Susan Cleaves; bride Almina M. Stoddard, parents David and Abigail Stoddard.
